::: details Ensure {{ $frontmatter.title }} Addon is enabled
Assuming Essentials has been [properly installed](/essentials-for-yootheme-pro/#installation), open the `Customizer -> Essentials -> Advanced` section and make sure **{{ $frontmatter.title }} Addon** is enabled, then save the changes and refresh the page.

![Enable {{ $frontmatter.title }} Addon](./assets/enable-addon.gif)

<small>
Notice that {{ $frontmatter.title }} is a premium addon and will not be listed if you are working with Essentials free version.
</small>
:::
